<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>{مُدْبِرِينَ <span class="c2">(٥٢)</span>} <span class="c4">[٥٢]</span> كاف.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{عَنْ ضَلَالَتِهِمْ}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٣]</span> حسن،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«بآياتنا»</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>{مُسْلِمُونَ <span class="c2">(٥٣)</span>} <span class="c4">[٥٣]</span> تام.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{مِنْ ضَعْفٍ}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٤]</span> جائز،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«قوة»</span>، وكذا <span class="c2">«وشيبة»</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{مَا يَشَاءُ}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٤]</span> كاف.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>{الْقَدِيرُ <span class="c2">(٥٤)</span>} <span class="c4">[٥٤]</span> تام.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c3">{الْمُجْرِمُونَ}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٥]</span> ليس بوقف؛ لأنَّ الذي بعده جواب القسم،<span class="c5"> وهو:</span> <span class="c2">«ما لبثوا»</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c3">{غَيْرَ سَاعَةٍ}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٥]</span> حسن.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>{يُؤْفَكُونَ <span class="c2">(٥٥)</span>} <span class="c4">[٥٥]</span> كاف،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«إلى يوم البعث»</span> لاختلاف الجملتين،<span class="c5"> والفاء في قوله:</span> <span class="c2">«فهذا يوم البعث»</span>، جواب شرط مقدر يدل عليه الكلام،<span class="c5"> تقديره:</span> إن كنتم شاكين، أو منكرين في يوم البعث فهذا يوم البعث <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>و <span class="c3">{يَوْمِ الْبَعْثِ}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٦]</span> ليس بوقف؛ لحرف الاستدراك بعده.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>{لَا تَعْلَمُونَ <span class="c2">(٥٦)</span>} <span class="c4">[٥٦]</span> كاف.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c3">{مَعْذِرَتُهُمْ}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٧]</span> جائز.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>{يُسْتَعْتَبُونَ <span class="c2">(٥٧)</span>} <span class="c4">[٥٧]</span> تام.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c3">{مِنْ كُلِّ مَثَلٍ}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٨]</span> كاف.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c3">{بِآَيَةٍ}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٨]</span> ليس بوقف؛ لأنَّ ما بعده قد قام مقام جواب القسم والجزاء.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>{مُبْطِلُونَ <span class="c2">(٥٨)</span>} <span class="c4">[٥٨]</span> حسن.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
